title: Kocky - Tricks
description:
Kocky&#039;s second singel from the highly praised debutalbum "Kingdom Came".The track features singer Rosanna, ex-member from girlgroup Play."Tricks" is the most beautiful and modern r&#039;n&#039;b coming out of Sweden ever. This is the first release with Rosanna going solo.
